ComicInfo.Summary:
Kaijumax guard Jin-Wook Jeong's low-level smog-smuggling gig has gone sour, and he begins scrambling to extricate himself without endangering his family. After a frightening encounter, Dr. Zhang's friendship with Torgax, the Terror of Anchorage, becomes something more. Meanwhile, a gang of would-be Elder Gods tooling up for a fight means a lucrative sword-selling business for the Lady of the Lake. Also: Blood-spattered walls! A frantic race against time! And... a dramatic resignation?
